findUnique

  where: {
    // ... provide filter here
  }
})

// Get one Client

  where: {
    // ... provide filter here
  }
})

Input

Name Type Required
where ClientWhereInput No
orderBy ClientOrderByWithRelationInput[] | ClientOrderByWithRelationInput No

Type: Client
Required: No
List: No
